com.github.princesslana.eriscasper.rest

Class ImmutableRoute.Builder<Rq,Rs>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.princesslana.eriscasper.rest.ImmutableRoute.Builder<Rq,Rs>
  • Enclosing class:
    ImmutableRoute<Rq,Rs>

    @NotThreadSafe
public static final class ImmutableRoute.Builder<Rq,Rs>
extends java.lang.Object
    Builds instances of type ImmutableRoute. Initialize attributes and then invoke the build() method to create an immutable instance.

    Builder is not thread-safe and generally should not be stored in a field or collection, but instead used immediately to create instances.
